OBJECTIVE OF THE PROGRAM

The system is capabale in keeping the important details of a costumers and also to stock the day to day transactions. The major objectives
of the system is to alter the traditional way of shopping by the use of Internet. They can now allow to buy items and articles of their
desire from the store.
This is some of the advantage of the system : 
* Shop 24/7
* Don't have to drag kids out
* Privacy
* Comparison Shopping easier
* Usability and easy access
